@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
participant "mobile-service" as MobileService
database "PostgreSQL Mobile DB" as MobileDB
database "MySQL Customer DB" as CustomerDB

Customer -> Gateway: POST /api/customers/cart/items/
Gateway -> CustomerService: POST /customers/cart/items/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> MobileService: GET /mobiles/{id}/
MobileService -> MobileDB: Check product, price, stock
MobileDB --> MobileService: Mobile detail
MobileService --> CustomerService: Mobile detail
CustomerService -> CustomerDB: Save cart item snapshot
CustomerDB --> CustomerService: Cart item row
CustomerService --> Gateway: Add item success
Gateway --> Customer: Cart item created
@enduml
